{
  "stem": "935.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The sculptors were not allowed to exhibit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then the Jews were not allowed to ride taxis anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then they weren't allowed to ride trams anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had somebody there who was running the theater and he somehow managed to get permission to turn this theater into a Jewish theater.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It became the Jewish theater-- the Joodsche Schouwburg-- with the understanding that only Jewish artists were performing on stage.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Only Jewish artists in the orchestra, only Jewish costume designer, choreographers, anything which had to do was in this, and for Jewish audiences only.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because we all had IDs, which you had to show.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And because of this, we had of course, incredible, incredible, entertainment there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because you couldn't have afforded to hire even half of these people under normal circumstances, what was now on the stage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had the soloists in the orchestra, and we had the best choreographers, and we had the best costume and set designers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the audiences, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They couldn't wait to get to our theater.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There came a time when these tickets sold on the black market for a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the Christians, the non-Jews, bought these tickets and borrowed a Jewish ID card to get into it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So any time you looked through the curtain, you saw faces.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the average were not Jews, going in there with a friend's Jewish ID card.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a totally reversed role.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was then a while when we got a Nazi sitting in our loge every night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a lot played in Dutch, so he didn't understand most of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was also that whatever you said on stage has been censored.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
